It's a big storehouse,

256
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:30,400
stores everything as karmic seeds.

257
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,700
As you can see,

258
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:33,100
the minor,

259
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,200
medium,

