00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,200
major,

261
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:38,600
secondary unwholesome mental factors,

262
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:41,500
these are not based on the severity,

263
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:42,800
of the affliction.

264
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:46,300
They are based on the range of function

265
00:14:46,300 --> 00:14:49,000
in the eight consciousnesses.

266
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:51,300
The minor one is called minor,

267
00:14:51,300 --> 00:14:54,900
because it's only working in the sixth consciousness.

268
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:57,500
The medium one is called medium,

269
00:14:57,500 --> 00:15:00,400
because it's in the first five consciousnesses,

270
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:02,300
and the sixth consciousnesses.

271
00:15:02,300 --> 00:15:04,700
And the major one is called major,

272
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:07,200
because it's in the first five,

273
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,800
and the sixth consciousnesses,

274
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,500
and the seventh consciousnesses.

275
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:11,200
Therefore,

276
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,900
the range is bigger,

277
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:15,000
that's why it's called major.

278
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:21,200
If we can understand these 26 unwholesome mental factors,

279
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:25,100
always be mindful of our thoughts,

280
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:27,400
and be able to catch them early,

281
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:32,200
we are able to purify our consciousnesses,

282
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:37,200
and transform the deluded consciousnesses into wisdom.

283
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:40,000
That's how we change from a mundane

284
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:40,800
to

285
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,000
a Buddha.

286
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,800
Everyone can do this.

287
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:44,600
Why?

288
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:49,000
Because the eighth consciousness is actually our Buddha nature.

289
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:51,200
Just wake up and purify it.

290
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:54,500
All the unwholesome mental factors,

